Package: redeemR
Title: Downstream Analysis for ReDeeM Mitochondrial Variant Calls
Version: 2.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Chen", "Weng", , "cweng@broadinstitute.org", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0801-7037"))
Author: Chen Weng [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0801-7037>)
Maintainer: Chen Weng <cweng@broadinstitute.org>
Description: Processes REDEEM-V mitochondrial consensus variant calls into filtered, annotated, quality-controlled objects for single-cell lineage analysis. redeemR2.0 provides post-consensus filtering, edge trimming, binomial noise filtering, variant annotation, quality control, matrix construction, and utilities for downstream lineage reconstruction and multiome integration.
